d":178203,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:13:39.000Z","msg":"馬利安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e392ddf8c70e61099a644d60fa13fcbd6133b778","tid":178203,"uid":93344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，最近跟班fd打籃球<br />\n本身冇籃球底，所以射波都只係推波咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推上去十粒有六七粒係入<br />\n後來有個打咗好耐嘅fd話我姿勢錯哂<br />\n應該左手輔助住，右手又唔知點整個旋出嚟<br />\n練練下發現一球都入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用返原本推波嘅方法，十粒可能入三四粒左右<br />\n退步咗勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外有時打比賽個陣攞到粒波淨係敢控住搵機會傳比隊友<br />\n完全唔敢射或者上籃<br />\n點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用腳力跳起再用手指將個波旋出去<br />\n利申 我打咁多年都係推 我唔夠力射 好耐之前跟過一個巴打練 失敗左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解比賽唔敢自己上？冇信心？</blockquote><br />\n腳力跳起係咪姐係jump shot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇錯，冇信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，射波係用腳力，正如上面有巴打都係咁講。<br />\njump shot唔同架<br />\n落街場多d就解決到問題，我跟校隊練，打小前逼住一定要射同做箭頭，過人就更加<br />\n試多幾次自然有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6cf3d9644b67912be9b7cf2e756423e2f81513","tid":178203,"uid":93344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>射波隻手 三個90度 手腕 手臂 腋下 另外果隻側面扶住 射嘅時候 由腳帶動手向上 扣腕 chop</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b666d1a226b747a38be294ac686e0214c6dbbf","tid":178203,"uid":33059,"like":0