手 三個90度 手腕 手臂 腋下 另外果隻側面扶住 射嘅時候 由腳帶動手向上 扣腕 chop</blockquote><br />\n好似又唔係幾難"},{"pid":"d709b1476c278df98b266380b4e83c145a63866f","tid":178203,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"睇入樽睇下櫻木點練"},{"pid":"b0cfda9adfd37e36b7dd098cd0419aa21558e915","tid":178203,"uid":74460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:44:09.000Z","msg":"認真講句，<br />\n射波最緊要入，<br />\n型唔型唔係重點，<br />\n唔入既話你射黎做乜？<br />\n你睇波想睇人入定AIR？"},{"pid":"26868dce60cefa37c7e55b24b3b8e24db75b8634","tid":178203,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:45:34.000Z","msg":"自己鐘意點射就點射<br />\n最緊要入<br />\n強如curry 都係推波"},{"pid":"cc6b48e3c216d34c30ebda0a64e4f5f203fe94b7","tid":178203,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真講句，<br />\n射波最緊要入，<br />\n型唔型唔係重點，<br />\n唔入既話你射黎做乜？<br />\n你睇波想睇人入定AIR？</blockquote><br />\n咁就緊係入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f87471e1757dfb2f2360bc5fdceb120e82a9e6","tid":178203,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:47:09.000Z","msg":"左手只係輔助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非你左手射球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9bef31fe97f048f62e2e2de8521d9e902fc5027","tid":178203,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:50:09.000Z","msg":"除咗射波，有冇巴打講下點訓練自己咩時候應該做D咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似要mark人，應該係跟實佢，係佢前面定係跟實將佢保持係視線範圍內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8592f8d3ac2289a7bd52b1892b715c48e5a658","tid":178203,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推介pro shot shooting YouTube <br />\n其實射波唔洗好大力<br />\n有個技巧係到慢慢練一定得<br />\n唔好太心急</blockquote><br />\n收