食指同中指旋轉個波 左手就只係輕輕扶住個波 加上少少腳向前既跳躣力 就係一般既射波動作</blockquote><br />\n放額頭已經係柒<br />\n之後重話要跳前射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8e9e57396dc9ef8be5ed67318c3a2ad56dcb8d","tid":178203,"uid":72524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:37:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔識點樣將個波射完係會係咁轉。。<br />\n但射姿都算正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上youtube睇jordan教射啦</blockquote><br />\n手指射<br />\n手心唔掂籃球</blockquote><br />\n其實轉太多係on9<br />\n正常射手係唔會落太多西</blockquote><br />\n型d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實轉多d都唔會太差 掂到框時力會削左容易滴返入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb6b743ae13bb6fa6491849c513f8cfa9af156d","tid":178203,"uid":72524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實推波比起射波有乜缺點??<br />\n推波出手好似快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快係練得出 推都射都得 curry快到好似推但其實佢真係射唔係推"},{"pid":"0e1fe27afd39b6d711d20153ead1969738344810","tid":178203,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔識點樣將個波射完係會係咁轉。。<br />\n但射姿都算正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上youtube睇jordan教射啦</blockquote><br />\n手指射<br />\n手心唔掂籃球</blockquote><br />\n其實轉太多係on9<br />\n正常射手係唔會落太多西</blockquote><br />\n型d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實轉多d都唔會太差 掂到框時力會削左容易滴返入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兄弟，我地係咪生處平行時空<br />\n落場d 框硬到少少西都彈到舞雷公咁遠wor"},{"pid":"ec13f407d3b96917e00b38913fd13b8e80fae383","tid":178203,"uid":72524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，最近跟班fd打籃球<br />\n本身冇籃球底，所以射波都只係推波咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推上去十粒有六七粒係入<br />\n後來有個打咗好耐嘅fd話我姿勢錯哂<br />\n應該左手輔助住，右手又唔知點整個旋出嚟<br />\n練練下發現一球都入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用返原本推波嘅方法，十粒可能入三四粒左右<br />\n退步咗勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外有時打比賽個陣攞到粒波淨係敢控住搵機會傳比隊友<br />\n完全唔敢射或者上籃<br />\n點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做你對面隊一定好開心見到你呢d 揀你mark可以回氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你諗下人地係咁諗就應該會唔忿氣 想挑戰佢<br />\n點都突破幾下 又可以猜下空位 又有機會得分"},{"pid":"a0028befa55c3b52d78e15220a5e60f6a3471fdc","tid":178203,"uid":52708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔識點樣將個波射完係會係咁轉。。<br />\n但射姿都算正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上youtube睇jordan教射啦</blockquote><br />\n手指射<br />\n手心唔掂籃球</blockquote><br />\n唔係話亞洲人手比較細手心少少掂到籃球都可以接受咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac86a5fd6b524d3f1bf10a88f9b6802a44063b5","tid":178203,"uid":13874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔識點樣將個波射完係會係咁轉。。<br />\n但射姿都算正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上youtube睇jordan教射啦</blockquote><br />\n手指射<br />\n手心唔掂籃球</blockquote><br />\n唔係話亞洲人手比較細手心少少掂到籃球都可以接受咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n少少都ok掛 唔好用手心發力就得"},{"pid":"b3d6dc38a0fdf70fc46e80671e7484b4d03d3c2e","tid":178203,"uid":6989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/playyuki/1333865310-413654446